<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
    <%= render partial: "styling" %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%= render partial: "header" %>
<div class='flip-button'>
  <%= mailer_user_events_link(@user, 'View pending forms') %>
</div>

    <p>
<% if @items.size > 1 -%>
The following events are getting close and still have forms awaiting
your input.  Please complete the forms so that the requested resources
can be allocated.
<% else -%>
The following event is getting close and still has a form awaiting
your input.  Please complete the form so that the requested resources
can be allocated.
<% end -%>
    </p>

<%= render @items %>

<p>
If you would prefer not to receive these messages, you can disable them
by editing your user record in Scheduler.  Log in and then click on your
name at the top right of the screen to do this.
</p>
  </body>
</html>
